{"tid":312362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過比無良通柒佬搵笨","createTime":"2017-07-07T11:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T14:50:06.000Z","uid":27663,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c6b43b36346472526bd17769feefad569b148e","tid":312362,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"[是咁的]<br />\n屋企個浴缸同洗手盤去水慢左<br />\n於是家姐搵左通渠佬上黎搞，傾好左$500 一次<br />\n點知上到黎係咁改價錢<br />\n<br />\n通渠佬就話因爲個浴缸同洗手盤分開兩次收費<br />\n(乜有浴缸唔係同洗手盤分開咩？)<br />\n咁家姐都ok，諗住之前傾得唔清楚<br />\n跟住整整下又唔對路<br />\n話要用咩高壓機整，原價一萬蚊，而家就平比家姐 $8000，<br />\n唔整今晚涼都沖唔到（但明明本身一直沖到）<br />\n<br />\n講到咁已經知伏味濃，<br />\n家姐就拒絕然後比返一開始既人工佢($1000)<br />\n咁好啦<br />\n一個係廳收錢寫收據，一個就匿係廁所執手尾<br />\n送完佢地走之後就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發現今朝新換既廁紙得返半卷<br />\n本身浴缸只係去水慢，而家完全去唔到水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後用廁所泵係浴缸泵咗成堆廁紙出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後順手撩埋本身d淤塞物出黎，通晒 <br />\n利申冇用過高壓機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652357544549e11ae312b0c76e4a02aef1d2151b","tid":312362,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"fb:香港專業通渠技術工程<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/call60343916/?fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcall60343916%2F%3Ffref%3Dnf&d=eMZntT2KeQ%2FrWnFhImo7sDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=04adff41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/call60343916/?fref=nf</a><br />\n<br />\n個無良通柒佬既fb <br />\n希望唔會再有巴絲比佢地搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da935d2cb24847328d90ddce543a4e7d7fc26cf5","tid":312362,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dcf763f37a4b184059f776f432e6394e77f2087","tid":312362,"uid":11171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩撚野通柒呀  渠就渠啦</blockquote><br />\n先唔講你單野<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 <br />\n<br />\n通渠就通渠啦 你覺得你將個渠字打做柒字好撚潮？好撚型？ 好撚與時俱進？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚見人地講慣左錯別字就走去跟啦 跟又跟得柒過人<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 肯撚定係00後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac38f406264b1cd50c45000ea85300e54ad34d3c","tid":312362,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"咁仆街"},{"pid":"9836b81b1eea9b81edc07cb5a6e296ad28a55968","tid":312362,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩撚野通柒呀  渠就渠啦</blockquote><br />\nsorry 大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嬲得滯打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b43ba48205deb359e44d157a7af2f94be4b4b4d","tid":312362,"uid":69335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"醒目嘅歌士的+熱水(逐少逐少落) 搞點喇"},{"pid":"4227c51433de19ca2282211f241b85b49767b1c0","tid":312362,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"叫人通渠收500，2日後又塞過，最後換座廁，先知有塊膠片跌左座廁入面"},{"pid":"e55c685f9c40e3002adca1f0f2314f24765c5cd9","tid":312362,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫人通渠收500，2日後又塞過，最後換座廁，先知有塊膠片跌左座廁入面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換座廁使左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e585c6b0c9882c0becdc8a8edf2ecb9e7cac12","tid":312362,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"呢行太多冇料扮四條喇。因為蝦外人唔識野，是旦搞兩搞話OK你都吹佢唔賬。"}]}